{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2430,"text":"This sound,"},{"time":5853,"text":"this smell,"},{"time":9588,"text":"this sight"},{"time":13693,"text":"all remind me of the campfires of my childhood,"},{"time":17221,"text":"when anyone could become a storyteller in front of the dancing flames."},{"time":24617,"text":"There was this wondrous ending"},{"time":27540,"text":"when people and fire fell asleep almost in unison."},{"time":32106,"text":"It was dreaming time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":36087,"text":"Now my story has a lot to do with dreaming,"},{"time":39424,"text":"although I'm known to make my dreams come true."},{"time":43134,"text":"Last year, I created a one-man show."},{"time":46425,"text":"For an hour and a half I shared with the audience"},{"time":50658,"text":"a lifetime of creativity,"},{"time":53325,"text":"how I pursue perfection, how I cheat the impossible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":57759,"text":"And then TED challenged me:"},{"time":60108,"text":"\"Philippe, can you shrink this lifetime to 18 minutes?\""},{"time":63273,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":64663,"text":"Eighteen minutes, clearly impossible."},{"time":68190,"text":"But here I am."},{"time":70453,"text":"One solution was to rehearse a machine gun delivery"},{"time":72815,"text":"in which every syllable, every second will have its importance"},{"time":75016,"text":"and hope to God the audience will be able to follow me."},{"time":76781,"text":"No, no, no."},{"time":78199,"text":"No, the best way for me to start"},{"time":81080,"text":"is to pay my respects to the gods of creativity."},{"time":84749,"text":"So please join me for a minute of silence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106026,"text":"Okay, I cheated, it was a mere 20 seconds."},{"time":108186,"text":"But hey, we're on TED time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110904,"text":"When I was six years old,"},{"time":112961,"text":"I fell in love with magic."},{"time":115759,"text":"For Christmas I got a magic box"},{"time":118178,"text":"and a very old book on card manipulation."},{"time":122633,"text":"Somehow I was more interested in pure manipulation"},{"time":125786,"text":"than in all the silly little tricks in the box."},{"time":130019,"text":"So I looked in the book for the most difficult move,"},{"time":133285,"text":"and it was this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136907,"text":"Now I'm not supposed to share that with you,"},{"time":138800,"text":"but I have to show you the card is hidden in the back of the hand."},{"time":144097,"text":"Now that manipulation"},{"time":146600,"text":"was broken down into seven moves"},{"time":150060,"text":"described over seven pages."},{"time":153174,"text":"One, two, three,"},{"time":155769,"text":"four, five, six and seven."},{"time":159383,"text":"And let me show you something else."},{"time":160984,"text":"The cards were bigger than my hands."}]},{"cues":[{"time":171433,"text":"Two months later, six years old,"},{"time":174036,"text":"I'm able to do one, two, three, four, five, six, seven."},{"time":177295,"text":"And I go to see a famous magician"},{"time":179435,"text":"and proudly ask him, \"Well what do you think?\""},{"time":182161,"text":"Six years old."},{"time":183501,"text":"The magician looked at me and said, \"This is a disaster."},{"time":186883,"text":"You cannot do that in two seconds"},{"time":189769,"text":"and have a minuscule part of the card showing."},{"time":193234,"text":"For the move to be professional, it has to be less than one second"},{"time":198718,"text":"and it has to be perfect.\""},{"time":202840,"text":"Two years later, one -- zoop."},{"time":207453,"text":"And I'm not cheating. It's in the back. It's perfect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215270,"text":"Passion is the motto"},{"time":221639,"text":"of all my actions."},{"time":223831,"text":"As I'm studying magic,"},{"time":228041,"text":"juggling is mentioned repeatedly"},{"time":230658,"text":"as a great way to acquire dexterity and coordination."},{"time":235226,"text":"Now I had long admired how fast and fluidly"},{"time":239541,"text":"jugglers make objects fly."},{"time":241775,"text":"So that's it. I'm 14; I'm becoming a juggler."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245703,"text":"I befriend a young juggler in a juggling troupe,"},{"time":249491,"text":"and he agrees to sell me three clubs."},{"time":253942,"text":"But in America you have to explain. What are clubs?"},{"time":256109,"text":"Nothing to do with golf."},{"time":257625,"text":"They are those beautiful oblong objects,"},{"time":262159,"text":"but quite difficult to make."},{"time":263759,"text":"They have to be precisely lathed."},{"time":265625,"text":"Oh, when I was buying the clubs,"},{"time":267793,"text":"somehow the young juggler was hiding from the others."},{"time":270942,"text":"Well I didn't think much of it at the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":273292,"text":"Anyway, here I was progressing with my new clubs."},{"time":277258,"text":"But I could not understand."},{"time":279594,"text":"I was pretty fast, but I was not fluid at all."},{"time":283360,"text":"The clubs were escaping me at each throw."},{"time":286542,"text":"And I was trying constantly to bring them back to me."},{"time":289559,"text":"Until one day I practiced in front of Francis Brunn,"},{"time":293692,"text":"the world's greatest juggler."},{"time":295860,"text":"And he was frowning."},{"time":297375,"text":"And he finally asked, \"Can I see those?\""},{"time":299792,"text":"So I proudly showed him my clubs."},{"time":302158,"text":"He said, \"Philippe, you have been had."},{"time":304575,"text":"These are rejects. They are completely out of alignment."},{"time":307976,"text":"They are impossible to juggle.\""},{"time":313127,"text":"Tenacity is how I kept at it"},{"time":319492,"text":"against all odds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321374,"text":"So I went to the circus to see more magicians, more jugglers,"},{"time":324926,"text":"and I saw -- oh no, no, no, I didn't see."},{"time":327408,"text":"It was more interesting; I heard."},{"time":329326,"text":"I heard about those amazing men and women"},{"time":331693,"text":"who walk on thin air --"},{"time":334378,"text":"the high-wire walkers."},{"time":337234,"text":"Now I have been playing with ropes and climbing all my childhood,"},{"time":340896,"text":"so that's it. I'm 16; I'm becoming a wire walker."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345619,"text":"I found two trees --"},{"time":350092,"text":"but not any kind of trees,"},{"time":352278,"text":"trees with character --"},{"time":354747,"text":"and then a very long rope."},{"time":356496,"text":"And I put the rope around and around"},{"time":358281,"text":"and around and around and around till I had no more rope."},{"time":360746,"text":"Now I have all of those ropes parallel like this."},{"time":363263,"text":"I get a pair of pliers and some coat hangers,"},{"time":365783,"text":"and I gather them together in some kind of ropey path."},{"time":371215,"text":"So I just created the widest tightrope in the world."},{"time":374833,"text":"What did I need? I needed the widest shoes in the world."},{"time":378311,"text":"So I found some enormous, ridiculous, giant ski boots"},{"time":382150,"text":"and then wobbly, wobbly I get on the ropes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":385333,"text":"Well within a few days I'm able to do one crossing."},{"time":389344,"text":"So I cut one rope off."},{"time":391387,"text":"And the next day one rope off."},{"time":393132,"text":"And a few days later, I was practicing on a single tightrope."},{"time":397931,"text":"Now you can imagine at that time"},{"time":399731,"text":"I had to switch the ridiculous boots for some slippers."},{"time":404165,"text":"So that is how -- in case there are people here in the audience who would like to try --"},{"time":409132,"text":"this is how not to learn wire walking."}]},{"cues":[{"time":412602,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":414116,"text":"Intuition is a tool essential in my life."},{"time":422648,"text":"In the meantime, I am being thrown out of five different schools"},{"time":427266,"text":"because instead of listening to the teachers,"},{"time":428934,"text":"I am my own teacher, progressing in my new art"},{"time":432965,"text":"and becoming a street juggler."}]},{"cues":[{"time":436099,"text":"On the high wire, within months,"},{"time":438750,"text":"I'm able to master all the tricks they do in the circus,"},{"time":441432,"text":"except I am not satisfied."}]},{"cues":[{"time":444015,"text":"I was starting to invent my own moves and bring them to perfection."},{"time":452276,"text":"But nobody wanted to hire me."},{"time":454980,"text":"So I started putting a wire up in secret and performing without permission."},{"time":460399,"text":"Notre Dame,"},{"time":464285,"text":"the Sydney Harbor Bridge,"},{"time":468323,"text":"the World Trade Center."},{"time":471417,"text":"And I developed a certitude, a faith"},{"time":473690,"text":"that convinced me that I will get safely to the other side."},{"time":477250,"text":"If not, I will never do that first step."}]},{"cues":[{"time":480002,"text":"Well nonetheless,"},{"time":482201,"text":"on the top of the World Trade Center"},{"time":485214,"text":"my first step was terrifying."},{"time":493111,"text":"All of a sudden the density of the air is no longer the same."},{"time":497384,"text":"Manhattan no longer spreads its infinity."},{"time":500220,"text":"The murmur of the city dissolves into a squall"},{"time":503500,"text":"whose chilling power I no longer feel."},{"time":507233,"text":"I lift the balancing pole. I approach the edge."},{"time":510099,"text":"I step over the beam."},{"time":511831,"text":"I put my left foot on the cable,"},{"time":515229,"text":"the weight of my body raised on my right leg"},{"time":518598,"text":"anchored to the flank of the building."},{"time":521878,"text":"Shall I ever so slightly shift my weight to the left?"},{"time":525697,"text":"My right leg will be unburdened,"},{"time":528214,"text":"my right foot will freely meet the wire."},{"time":531717,"text":"On one side, a mass of a mountain, a life I know."},{"time":536289,"text":"On the other, the universe of the clouds,"},{"time":539014,"text":"so full of unknown we think it's empty."},{"time":542582,"text":"At my feet, the path to the north tower -- 60 yards of wire rope."},{"time":548797,"text":"It's a straight line, which sags,"},{"time":552178,"text":"which sways, which vibrates,"},{"time":555699,"text":"which rolls on itself,"},{"time":557263,"text":"which is ice,"},{"time":558998,"text":"which is three tons tight, ready to explode,"},{"time":563367,"text":"ready to swallow me."},{"time":565981,"text":"An inner howl assails me,"},{"time":568947,"text":"the wild longing to flee."},{"time":571964,"text":"But it is too late."},{"time":574431,"text":"The wire is ready."},{"time":577081,"text":"Decisively my other foot sets itself onto the cable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":589718,"text":"Faith is what replaces doubt"},{"time":594213,"text":"in my dictionary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":596243,"text":"So after the walk"},{"time":597469,"text":"people ask me, \"How can you top that?\""},{"time":599313,"text":"Well I didn't have that problem."},{"time":601618,"text":"I was not interested in collecting the gigantic,"},{"time":604220,"text":"in breaking records."},{"time":606302,"text":"In fact, I put my World Trade Center crossing"},{"time":611331,"text":"at the same artistic level as some of my smaller walks --"},{"time":614881,"text":"or some completely different type of performance."},{"time":619797,"text":"Let's see, such as my street juggling, for example."}]},{"cues":[{"time":625959,"text":"So each time"},{"time":628427,"text":"I draw my circle of chalk on the pavement"},{"time":631648,"text":"and enter as the improvising comic silent character"},{"time":636491,"text":"I created 45 years ago,"},{"time":638416,"text":"I am as happy as when I am in the clouds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":642463,"text":"But this here,"},{"time":644418,"text":"this is not the street."},{"time":646749,"text":"So I cannot street juggle here, you understand."},{"time":649325,"text":"So you don't want me to street juggle here, right?"},{"time":651498,"text":"You know that, right?"},{"time":652864,"text":"You don't want me to juggle, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":655113,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":663335,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":775200,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":780238,"text":"Thank you. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":794720,"text":"Each time I street juggle"},{"time":797672,"text":"I use improvisation."},{"time":808765,"text":"Now improvisation is empowering"},{"time":810967,"text":"because it welcomes the unknown."},{"time":815167,"text":"And since what's impossible is always unknown,"},{"time":819299,"text":"it allows me to believe I can cheat the impossible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":826889,"text":"Now I have done the impossible not once,"},{"time":829333,"text":"but many times."},{"time":831518,"text":"So what should I share? Oh, I know. Israel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":833964,"text":"Some years ago I was invited to open the Israel Festival"},{"time":838635,"text":"by a high-wire walk."},{"time":840601,"text":"And I chose to put my wire"},{"time":842450,"text":"between the Arab quarters and the Jewish quarter of Jerusalem"},{"time":846453,"text":"over the Ben Hinnom Valley."},{"time":848384,"text":"And I thought it would be incredible"},{"time":850551,"text":"if in the middle of the wire"},{"time":852374,"text":"I stopped and, like a magician,"},{"time":854357,"text":"I produce a dove and send her in the sky"},{"time":858122,"text":"as a living symbol of peace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":860472,"text":"Well now I must say,"},{"time":863289,"text":"it was a little bit hard to find a dove in Israel, but I got one."},{"time":866273,"text":"And in my hotel room,"},{"time":869197,"text":"each time I practiced making it appear and throwing her in the air,"},{"time":874177,"text":"she would graze the wall and end up on the bed."},{"time":876796,"text":"So I said, now it's okay. The room is too small."},{"time":879561,"text":"I mean, a bird needs space to fly."},{"time":881310,"text":"It will go perfectly on the day of the walk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":883562,"text":"Now comes the day of the walk."},{"time":886943,"text":"Eighty thousand people spread over the entire valley."},{"time":890593,"text":"The mayor of Jerusalem, Teddy Kollek, comes to wish me the best."},{"time":895177,"text":"But he seemed nervous."},{"time":898062,"text":"There was tension in my wire,"},{"time":900311,"text":"but I also could feel tension on the ground."},{"time":902426,"text":"Because all those people"},{"time":903744,"text":"were made up of people who, for the most part,"},{"time":906843,"text":"considered each other enemies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":909728,"text":"So I start the walk. Everything is fine."},{"time":912464,"text":"I stop in the middle."},{"time":914242,"text":"I make the dove appear."},{"time":916961,"text":"People applaud in delight."},{"time":918877,"text":"And then in the most magnificent gesture,"},{"time":921646,"text":"I send the bird of peace into the azure."},{"time":925177,"text":"But the bird, instead of flying away,"},{"time":926926,"text":"goes flop, flop, flop and lands on my head."},{"time":929977,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":932061,"text":"And people scream."},{"time":933960,"text":"So I grab the dove,"},{"time":936578,"text":"and for the second time I send her in the air."},{"time":941374,"text":"But the dove, who obviously didn't go to flying school,"},{"time":944547,"text":"goes flop, flop, flop and ends up at the end of my balancing pole."}]},{"cues":[{"time":948594,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":949910,"text":"You laugh, you laugh. But hey."},{"time":952165,"text":"I sit down immediately. It's a reflex of wire walkers."},{"time":955594,"text":"Now in the meantime, the audience, they go crazy."},{"time":958813,"text":"They must think this guy with this dove,"},{"time":961177,"text":"he must have spent years working with him."},{"time":963343,"text":"What a genius, what a professional."}]},{"cues":[{"time":964760,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":966731,"text":"So I take a bow. I salute with my hand."},{"time":969710,"text":"And at the end I bang my hand against the pole"},{"time":971778,"text":"to dislodge the bird."},{"time":973295,"text":"Now the dove, who, now you know, obviously cannot fly,"},{"time":976944,"text":"does for the third time a little flop, flop, flop"},{"time":979695,"text":"and ends up on the wire behind me."},{"time":981728,"text":"And the entire valley goes crazy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":984744,"text":"Now but hold on, I'm not finished."},{"time":986827,"text":"So now I'm like 50 yards from my arrival"},{"time":989361,"text":"and I'm exhausted, so my steps are slow."},{"time":992010,"text":"And something happened."},{"time":993593,"text":"Somebody somewhere, a group of people,"},{"time":996062,"text":"starts clapping in rhythm with my steps."},{"time":999244,"text":"And within seconds the entire valley"},{"time":1001093,"text":"is applauding in unison with each of my steps."},{"time":1005077,"text":"But not an applause of delight like before,"},{"time":1007210,"text":"an applause encouragement."},{"time":1010594,"text":"For a moment, the entire crowd had forgotten their differences."},{"time":1014759,"text":"They had become one, pushing me to triumph."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1019708,"text":"I want you just for a second"},{"time":1022375,"text":"to experience this amazing human symphony."},{"time":1025388,"text":"So let's say I am here and the chair is my arrival."},{"time":1028524,"text":"So I walk, you clap, everybody in unison."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1032424,"text":"(Clapping)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1038638,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1045063,"text":"So after the walk, Teddy and I become friends."},{"time":1047919,"text":"And he tells me, he has on his desk a picture of me"},{"time":1051572,"text":"in the middle of the wire with a dove on my head."},{"time":1054007,"text":"He didn't know the true story."},{"time":1055424,"text":"And whenever he's daunted by an impossible situation"},{"time":1059072,"text":"to solve in this hard-to-manage city,"},{"time":1061472,"text":"instead of giving up, he looks at the picture and he says,"},{"time":1064490,"text":"\"If Philippe can do that, I can do this,\""},{"time":1066823,"text":"and he goes back to work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1070442,"text":"Inspiration."},{"time":1079468,"text":"By inspiring ourselves"},{"time":1081916,"text":"we inspire others."},{"time":1084106,"text":"I will never forget this music,"},{"time":1085889,"text":"and I hope now neither will you."},{"time":1088406,"text":"Please take this music with you home,"},{"time":1091138,"text":"and start gluing feathers to your arms"},{"time":1094644,"text":"and take off and fly,"},{"time":1096962,"text":"and look at the world from a different perspective."},{"time":1102970,"text":"And when you see mountains,"},{"time":1105415,"text":"remember mountains can be moved."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1108208,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1116340,"text":"Thank you. Thank you."},{"time":1119358,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1123030,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}